References: https://developer.hashicorp.com/nomad/tutorials/archive/variables-tasks 

Create Nomad variables:
nomad var put s1/foo u=1 p=p1

####### Create policy.hcl
namespace "default" {
  variables {
    path "*" {
      capabilities = ["read"]
    }
  }
}
################
Now, create the policy and associate it with the web task in the servers group of the hello-world job, specifying the appropriate flags on the nomad acl policy apply command.

nomad acl policy apply -namespace default -job hello-world -group servers -task web web-policy ./policy.hcl

To verify:
nomad acl policy info web-policy

#######
nomad job run job.hcl
